WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:12.400 --> 00:00:17.400
 - Our latest models are Lada Granta and Lada Largus. 

00:00:17.500 --> 00:00:21.000
 Lada Granta is a model developed within "AvtoVAZ". 

00:00:21.100 --> 00:00:24.100
 Over the past five months 

00:00:24.200 --> 00:00:28.000
 this car became the best-selling in Russia. 

00:00:28.100 --> 00:00:32.100
 This is the cheapest model in the "AvtoVAZ" range 

00:00:32.200 --> 00:00:36.200
 and its price ranges from 6700 euros upwards. 

00:00:36.300 --> 00:00:41.000
 Lada Granta is the first Russian car with automatic gearbox. 

00:00:41.100 --> 00:00:49.000
 intended for a wide range of customers. 

00:00:49.100 --> 00:00:52.700
 The second new model is Lada Largus. 

00:00:52.800 --> 00:00:56.500
 It is a multipurpose vehicle with increased transport capacity. 

00:00:56.600 --> 00:01:01.500
 The vehicle is made in 5 and 7-seater versions. 

00:01:01.600 --> 00:01:07.000
 No similar vehicle is produced in Russia. 

00:01:07.100 --> 00:01:12.000
 There is currently a great demand for this model, 

00:01:12.100 --> 00:01:17.100
 is very popular, especially considering the favorable price and quality relationship. 

00:01:17.200 --> 00:01:21.500
 Every day we produce over 2000 vehicles. 

00:01:21.600 --> 00:01:30.000
 During 2012 we produced over 550,000 cars. 

00:01:30.100 --> 00:01:34.100
 Cars "Lada" have their customers in Russia 

00:01:34.200 --> 00:01:38.200
 and most of the production is sold in the country. 

00:01:38.300 --> 00:01:42.300
 However, they are also sought abroad, 

00:01:42.400 --> 00:01:49.000
 primarily in neighboring countries, such as Kazakhstan, Ukraine, Belarus, Azerbaijan. 

00:01:49.100 --> 00:01:55.000
 Cars are delivered to Europe and Latin America. 

00:01:55.100 --> 00:02:00.000
 In "AvtoVAZ" the realization of the development program is in progress up to 2020. 

00:02:00.100 --> 00:02:05.100
 It is planned that by 2017 car production 

00:02:05.200 --> 00:02:11.000
 reaches 1.5 million vehicles annually. 

00:02:11.100 --> 00:02:15.100
 It will be the cars brand "Lada", "Renault" and "Nissan". 

00:02:15.200 --> 00:02:18.500
 Two-thirds of it will be the cars of the brand "Lada". 

